{
  "stem": "10644.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Through damage-- damage of the ovaries, and damage of the ovaries, and damage of the gametes, which is in the ovaries.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My dear, my dear, it is simple.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It could-- could affect, directly, the ovaries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If a woman is suddenly under severe emotional stress, she may stop menstruating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She may stop menstruating, and that is, if you want to ask why, because the ovaries are affected.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The ovaries are not producing, working normally, and you can expect everything [? that you want ?] possible-- maybe miscarriages, maybe malformations, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody was talking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was talking  about this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure-- kept alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I kept alive, and the Jewish committee even established a special place for all these malformed children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I will not say where it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Priskin, who was the director of all this told me, because I presented the results of these studies to-- at a convention of Jewish doctors.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right, fine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was somewhere beginning 1948.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, she could.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She could.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody compelled her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you must understand that these women-- if a child had, we'll say, some other handicaps-- I will give you an example.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nobody wants to stay in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some are going to South Africa.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some are going to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some are going to Canada, Australia-- Canada, a few.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The United States, too, was closed, until the Act of Displaced Persons came out, where they allowed 300,000 displaced persons to come to the United States.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But it is not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It is mostly Poles, mostly Russians, mostly Czechs, all from the east countries.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We didn't want to go back-- back to-- to Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That will not-- the Americans will not allow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you want in, either you live here, or you stay here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Stay here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Very many stayed with the children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My dear--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they had their-- their doctors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, also from a liberated-- liberated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One, for example, Doctor Herman-- he was a very good surgeon, but he worked at that time just checking all these things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, people were going to the United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had to check their health.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, never.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody-- nobody kills-- kills.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you kill, you killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It is an old crime.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are not allowed, as doctors, to kill abnormal children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked at the University Hospital in Munich for four or five years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I published a lot of scientific papers, all connected, mostly connected, with the concentration camp with a very strong response from other countries, even the Germans, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally, the Russians published their result, all confirming my findings.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I introduced that it is not nor usually acceptable to do [INAUDIBLE] if you damage an embryo already-- or you-- if you deliver, you didn't have-- naturally, a surgeon, it could be that you have inherited such a thing.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I introduced the term that it is plasmatic damage of the egg, that the plasma of the egg is damaged.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I couldn't define what it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could define, but it is the plasma of the egg is damaged.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the nucleus and the-- that was damaged.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hunger and severe emotional distress.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You cannot relate to this, but it is hunger and severe emotional distress.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's accepted all over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The-- the-- hold on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Four years after I published my papers, a paper appears in Sweden, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] where they studied, now, the cells-- ovarian cells, we'll say-- cells, the gametes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "First, they said it is not 48 chromosomes, but 46 chromosomes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they segregated in a very fine way-- these two America scientists, Tjio and Levan, they did these studies in Sweden at the University of Sweden.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Found?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't find.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] They found that-- they first went into the how a cell is built.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had-- we knew already it is 48 chromosomes, but they-- they did a beautiful job.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For me, they deserve to have a Nobel Prize.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now, you know, when this was established, now, in England, they started to study hormonal deficiencies in the babies.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe it is connected with the chromosomal status.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first [? full ?] did it on-- because most frequent-- in my papers was most frequent-- were mongoloids.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lejeune is the name of a scientist from-- in Paris.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He started to study the chromosomes in mongoloids.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here he found, you know, that instead of 46 chromosomes, they have 45 chromosomes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One chromosome is missing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'51.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure, with just one child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I married a woman-- a woman who I got acquainted with in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Galina Raicinska.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, sure after my wife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was three-- it was almost four years after she died.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
